# GitHub Linguist overrides — force correct language detection
# See: https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist/blob/main/docs/overrides.md

# Mark web scaffold as non-project code
web/** linguist-vendored

# Mark platform boilerplate as generated
linux/** linguist-generated
macos/** linguist-generated
windows/** linguist-generated
ios/** linguist-generated
android/app/src/main/res/** linguist-generated

# Ensure Dart is primary
*.dart linguist-language=Dart
